WITHDRAWALDESCRIPTION: The Registrant ceased its operation as a transfer agent on 4/30/10 in connection with the sale of a portion of Columbia Management's business to Ameriprise Financial Inc.
Security Benefit Life Insurance Company no longer performs the functions that required it to be registered as a transfer agent.
PacWest Transfer, LLC has sold all of its accounts and assets to another transfer agent and will not longer perform transfer agent functions.
